<h2 class="text-center">Functions</h2>            
<p>GCAVC functions as the official regulatory body for visually impaired chess players in Gujarat. It organizes various tournaments ranging from district to national levels, including the state selection tournament and the state team championship. The association also operates a chess academy at the Blind People’s Association in Ahmedabad, providing training materials and coaching to talented players across the state.</p>            
